<p>
<note n="0850002" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0850002">魏【大】，魏北【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0850003" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0850003">藏【大】，藏法師【宋】【元】【明】</note>
